Text:
I am sorry, this is a lecture, not a interview ;)
But still very good information, and important stuff...
Tack kille för din komment, men jag vet redan att Bill är ok. Har du sett alla videon med honom? Du borde se dem före du tvekar.

Why is it that you always get Wicca and Druidism mixed up with UFOs and Vampires?! Scientific wishful thinking and a blood disease have nothing to do with personal faith in any form.  Move our spirituality out of the new age section, and put in the Religion section next to the other 5 shelves of Christianity where it belongs!
